WEBVTT

04:33.733 --> 04:34.858
And so, in my eyes...

04:35.524 --> 04:36.983
everything I did was right.

04:38.483 --> 04:39.608
Please forgive us.

04:54.108 --> 04:55.441
Can you please...

04:55.899 --> 04:57.483
tell me where
it is, Georgekutty?

04:58.899 --> 05:00.358
I'll take it away in secret.

05:00.649 --> 05:01.816
Even Geetha won't know.

05:02.108 --> 05:03.691
Please don't come
to meet me again, sir.

05:04.524 --> 05:07.024
Don't drag us back to the
memories we're trying to forget.
